Outdoor Cats
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<POST>
<POSTER> Marshall D. Tessnear </POSTER>
<POSTDATE> 1999-03-09T12:00:00 </POSTDATE>
Email: &quot;Marshall D. Tessnear&quot;&lt;tessn ... @vt.edu&gt;
